---
const rawDomain = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_PROXY_DOMAIN ?? "";
const normalizedDomain = rawDomain.trim().replace(/\/+$/, "");
const hasDomain = normalizedDomain.length > 0;
const displayDomain = hasDomain ? normalizedDomain : "https://<proxy-domain>";

const mcArgs = [
  `-Dminecraft.api.auth.host=${displayDomain}/auth`,
  `-Dminecraft.api.account.host=${displayDomain}/account`,
  `-Dminecraft.api.session.host=${displayDomain}/session`,
  `-Dminecraft.api.services.host=${displayDomain}/services`,
  `-Dminecraft.api.profiles.host=${displayDomain}/profiles`,
];

const velocityArg = `-Dmojang.sessionserver=${displayDomain}/session/session/minecraft/hasJoined`;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Minecraft API 转发参数教程</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4f6f8;
        --panel: #ffffff;
        --text: #182430;
        --muted: #5a6a78;
        --accent: #0b8f6f;
        --warn-bg: #fff4d6;
        --warn-border: #f1ce74;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
          "PingFang SC", "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, #d8efe8 0%, transparent 42%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #eef3f6 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      }

      main {
        max-width: 920px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 18px 72px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--panel);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 28px 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(14, 36, 55, 0.08);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 30px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-top: 28px;
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      pre {
        margin: 12px 0 0;
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding: 14px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #d7dee5;
        background: #f8fafb;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      code {
        font-family: "SF Mono", Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
      }

      .muted {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .warn {
        margin-top: 14px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--warn-border);
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: var(--warn-bg);
      }

      a {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <article class="card">
        <h1>Minecraft API 转发参数教程</h1>
        <p class="muted">
          仅需在启动命令里把参数放到 <code>-jar</code> 之前，无需修改游戏。
        </p>

        {
          !hasDomain && (
            <div class="warn">
              未设置 `PUBLIC_PROXY_DOMAIN`，当前页面使用占位符
              `https://&lt;proxy-domain&gt;` 展示。
              <br />
              构建前请在环境变量中设置该值，例如：
              <code>PUBLIC_PROXY_DOMAIN=https://msp.example.com</code>
            </div>
          )
        }

        <h2>Minecraft 服务端 / 客户端</h2>
        <p>多行版本</p>
        <pre><code>{mcArgs.join("\n")}</code></pre>

        <p>一行版本（空格分隔）</p>
        <pre><code>{mcArgs.join(" ")}</code></pre>

        <p>
          适用于 MC 1.16+，也大概率适用于 Paper 等非原版端。即使高版本基本不用
          `auth`，低版本仍建议带上，确保整套转发配置生效。
        </p>

        <p>
          如果是 1.14 / 1.15 客户端，可尝试此 Backport 模组：
          <a href="https://github.com/Fallen-Breath/AuthlibEnvBackport"
            >AuthlibEnvBackport</a
          >
        </p>

        <h2>Velocity</h2>
        <p>
          仅需在启动 Velocity 的命令行参数里，在 <code>-jar</code> 参数前加入以下参数：
        </p>
        <pre><code>{velocityArg}</code></pre>
      </article>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
